	<text>
		<body xml:lang="en">
			<div>

	<pb n="0001" facs="liv_001276_0001"/><!--pb/@n='97r'-->
<lb/><p rend="right"><placeName>Birkenhead</placeName></p>
<lb/><p rend="right">6<hi rend="sup"><hi rend="underline">th</hi></hi> March 
<lb/>1858</p>
<lb/><p>My Dear <persName>M<hi rend="sup">r</hi> Murray</persName></p>
<lb/><p>The <term type="boat">Pearl</term> is 
<lb/>out of dock 
<lb/>and the launch 
<lb/>on board all 
<lb/>right. We 
<lb/>sail on Monday 

	<pb n="0002" facs="liv_001276_0002"/><!--pb/@n='97v'--> 
<lb/>next - forenoon<reg>.</reg>
<lb/>Any letters that 
<lb/>may come 
<lb/>had better be 
<lb/>sent  when 
<lb/>a parcel is 
<lb/>made up to 
<lb/><persName>Lenox Conyngham</persName>
<lb/>Foreign Office 
<lb/>he will forward 
<lb/>them to the <placeName>Cape</placeName><reg>.</reg>

	<pb n="0003" facs="liv_001276_0003"/><!--pb/@n='98r'--> 
<lb/>I am very much 
<lb/>knocked up 
<lb/>and will feel 
<lb/>glad when 
<lb/>away (the stomach 
<lb/>being calm) and 
<lb/>in finer 
<lb/>weather. I shall 
<lb/>write a note 
<lb/>additional 
<lb/>for <persName>M<hi rend="sup">r</hi> Elwin</persName>

	<pb n="0004" facs="liv_001276_0004"/><!--pb/@n='98v'--> 
<lb/>when I get time 
<lb/>about the ants 
<lb/>&amp; <del type="strikethrough">when</del> though thou 
<lb/>pray a fool in 
<lb/>a <gap extent="1" unit="words" agent="illegible"/> &amp;c<reg>.</reg></p>
<lb/><p>If <persName>M<hi rend="sup">r</hi> Cook</persName><unclear cert="low">gives</unclear>
<lb/><persName><unclear cert="low">Henry<reg>'</reg>s</unclear></persName> commentary 
<lb/>to <persName>M<hi rend="sup">r</hi> Young</persName><placeName>29 
<lb/>Oxford St.</placeName> he 
<lb/>will take care 
<lb/>of it. I have not 
<lb/>seen the Analysis 
<lb/>yet <add place="above">complete</add>. I am &amp;c 
<lb/><addSpan spanTo="#p97r" place="marginleft"><!--addSpan/@place='left margin of fos. 97r, 97v, 98r'--></addSpan>I am &amp;c David Livingstone<reg>.</reg></p>

	<pb n="0005" facs="liv_001276_0005"/><!--pb/@n='97v'-->
<lb/><p>Kindest regards to <persName>M<hi rend="sup"><hi rend="underline">rs</hi></hi> M.</persName></p>

	<pb n="0006" facs="liv_001276_0006"/><!--pb/@n='98r'-->
<lb/><p>If the Analysis complete 
<lb/>is sent it may be among 
<lb/>some unopened parcels<reg>.</reg></p><anchor xml:id="p97r"/>
			
</div>
